Comedian, MC Sweet Mouth led entertainers to the opening of a new hospitality outfit, APNO Hotel and Suite in the heart of Ibeju Lekki, Lagos. The new outfit opened to fun seekers and entertainment buffs on Saturday, February 29 and it had several entertainers thrilling guests. MC Sweet Mouth was joined on the stage by MC Shakara, Spider Rider, Mc Loudmouth, Mc Alleluyah, McVibes, Dr Wyfo, Wazobia Boys and West P to thrill guests. Speaking on the opening, the General Manager of the hospitality outfit, Chukwuma Chukwuemeka described the accommodation as a home of comfort and quality service that will make guests fall in love with the hospitality outfit.